Class TextData

    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.RawData

    UploadData 

    public class TextData
extends RawData
    Contains POST parameters which cannot be represented as FormData or MultipartFormData but can be represented as plain text.
    包含POST参数，这些参数不能表示为FormData或MultipartFormData，但可以表示为纯文本。
